title: Branch order is unrestricted.
pid: 04255a68-3d82-448b-88ba-a8ae1f612791
body: |2-
  Within any branch note,
  the order of its content notes is up to the user.
  It might be ordered by personal priority;
  it might be ordered for a new student;
  it might be designed as something enjoyable to meditate on.

  There can be multiple orders on the same notes.

  It might be hygienic to indicate how to interpret the order on each branch list, but the app does not make you do that.
